#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                The new period is not valid for some products of your cart.\n"
"                Your changes on the rental period are not taken into account.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ໄລຍະເວລາໃໝ່ໃຊ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ກັບບາງສິນຄ້າໃນກະຕ່າຂອງທ່ານ.\n"
"                ການປ່ຽນແປງໄລຍະເວລາການເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານຈະບໍ່ຖືກນຳມາຄິດໄລ່.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental duration was too short. Unfortunately, we do not process\n"
"                rentals that last less than %(duration)s %(unit)s.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ໄລຍະເວລາການເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານສັ້ນເກີນໄປ. ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດດຳເນີນການ\n"
"                ການເຊົ່າທີ່ໃຊ້ເວລາໜ້ອຍກວ່າ %(duration)s %(unit)s.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid date of pickup (%(start_date)s).\n"
"                Unfortunately, we do not process pickups on that weekday.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີຮັບເຄື່ອງບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (%(start_date)s).\n"
"                ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການຮັບເຄື່ອງໃນວັນນັ້ນຂອງອາທິດ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid date of return (%(end_date)s).\n"
"                Unfortunately, we do not process returns on that weekday.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີສົ່ງຄືນບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (%(end_date)s).\n"
"                ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການສົ່ງຄືນໃນວັນນັ້ນຂອງອາທິດ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"                Your rental product had invalid dates of pickup (%(start_date)s) and\n"
"                return (%(end_date)s). Unfortunately, we do not process pickups nor\n"
"                returns on those weekdays.\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                ສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານມີວັນທີຮັບເຄື່ອງ (%(start_date)s) ແລະ\n"
"                ວັນທີສົ່ງຄືນ (%(end_date)s) ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ມີການຮັບເຄື່ອງ ຫຼື\n"
"                ສົ່ງຄືນໃນວັນເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນຂອງອາທິດ.\n"
"            "

#. module: website_sale_renting
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/website_sale_renting/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Some of your rental products (%(product)s) cannot be rented during the\n"
"            selected period and your cart must be updated. We're sorry for the\n"
"            inconvenience.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            ບາງສິນຄ້າເຊົ່າຂອງທ່ານ (%(product)s) ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຫ້ເຊົ່າໄດ້ໃນ\n"
"            ໄລຍະເວລາທີ່ເລືອກ ແລະ ກະຕ່າຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດ. ຂໍອະໄພໃນ\n"
"            ຄວາມບໍ່ສະດວກ.\n"
"        "

